					United Kingdom
				</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 mobile-sm:mt-3 text-xl mobile-sm:text-2xl font-semibold text-white">UK Partners Hub</h2>
				<p class="mt-1.5 mobile-sm:mt-2 text-xs mobile-sm:text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
					If you are a partner, fleet operator or investor in the UK, we connect you with our local business development team to explore opportunities and tailored projects.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-4 mobile-sm:mt-5 mobile-lg:mt-6 space-y-1.5 mobile-sm:space-y-2 text-xs mobile-sm:text-sm text-white/80">
